Popular Abuja based-right activist Deji Adeyanju has reacted to the decision of APC 2023 presidential candidate Bola Ahmed Tinubu to pick a Muslim running mate for the 2023 presidential elections.
The controversial activist Deji Adeyanju, reacted on his official Facebook account. He stated that;
“Tinubu pick of Shettima is a very strong ticket
His VP pick will naturally deliver Borno State to him”
Here is Deji Adeyanju post on his official Facebook account;
Recall that according to punch newspapers, The APC 2023 presidential candidate and former governor of Lagos state Boma Ahmed Tinubu, had earlier announced Rashim Shettima the former governor of Borno State as his running mate on Sunday in Daura, Katsina State.
The APC 2023 presidential aspirant and former governor of Lagos Stated Bola Ahmed Tinubu stated that he picked the former governor of Borno state, Rashim Shettima because he is competent and has the ability to deliver.


